Subject to bank's Privacy Policy, you agree that bank may use, copy, modify, display and distribute any information, data, materials or other content (the "Content") you provide to bank for the purpose of providing the Service, and you hereby give bank a license to do so. By submitting Content, you represent that you have the right to license such Content to bank for the purposes set forth in this Agreement.
